      <text fn="Arial" fh="15" fc="16777215" fa="1" charset="238">. It is utilised in the vulcanisation of rubber and in the manufacture of matches, fireworks and gunpowder. Sulphur compounds are applied in medicine in the treatment of skin conditions, and in agriculture as pesticides. Sulphur is also used in the production of pigments and dyes.</text>
